{
  "uid": "h3-falha",
  "title": "H3 \u2014 Falha Parcial e Consist\u00eancia",
  "description": "Estado do sistema sob falha. Suporta H3: estado zombie, circuit breakers, lag Kafka.",
  "tags": [
    "xcommerce",
    "h3",
    "falha",
    "consistencia"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-15m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Estado dos Servi\u00e7os (UP/DOWN)",
      "description": "1 = UP, 0 = DOWN. Quando inventory-service for parado, deve aparecer 0.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 4
      },
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"xcommerce-microservices\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{ instance }}",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "DOWN",
                  "color": "red"
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "UP",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "orientation": "horizontal"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Circuit Breaker \u2014 estado por rota (gateway)",
      "description": "Estado do circuit breaker Resilience4j no gateway. CLOSED=normal, OPEN=a cortar pedidos, HALF_OPEN=a tentar recuperar. Durante H3, a rota do inventory deve abrir.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "resilience4j_circuitbreaker_state{job=\"xcommerce-microservices\"}",
          "legendFormat": "CB {{ name }} state={{ state }}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Circuit Breaker \u2014 chamadas bloqueadas (gateway)",
      "description": "Pedidos bloqueados pelo circuit breaker e enviados para o fallback. Spike durante H3 confirma que o gateway protege os outros servi\u00e7os.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(resilience4j_circuitbreaker_not_permitted_calls_total{job=\"xcommerce-microservices\"}[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "bloqueadas {{ name }}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Taxa de erros HTTP \u2014 por servi\u00e7o",
      "description": "Erros 5xx por servi\u00e7o. Durante H3 (inventory parado), o order-service pode devolver erros antes do circuit breaker abrir.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{job=\"xcommerce-microservices\", status=~\"5..\"}[1m])) by (instance)",
          "legendFormat": "5xx {{ instance }}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Lat\u00eancia p95 \u2014 order-service durante falha",
      "description": "Quando inventory-service est\u00e1 parado, o order-service aguarda timeout (5s) antes de falhar. Spike vis\u00edvel no p95.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_server_requests_seconds_sum{instance=\"order-service:8084\", uri!~\"/actuator.*\"}[1m]) / rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{instance=\"order-service:8084\", uri!~\"/actuator.*\"}[1m]) * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "avg order {{ uri }} (ms)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Kafka \u2014 mensagens produzidas vs consumidas (order-created-events)",
      "description": "Quando inventory-service est\u00e1 parado, as mensagens produzidas acumulam sem ser consumidas. Lag vis\u00edvel aqui (se o Kafka expuser m\u00e9tricas via JMX exporter).",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "kafka_consumer_fetch_manager_records_consumed_rate{job=\"xcommerce-microservices\"}",
          "legendFormat": "consumed {{ client_id }}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "kafka_producer_record_send_rate{job=\"xcommerce-microservices\"}",
          "legendFormat": "produced {{ client_id }}",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Health checks \u2014 falhas por servi\u00e7o",
      "description": "Falhas de health check reportadas pelo Spring Actuator. Complementa o painel UP/DOWN com granularidade por componente (DB, Kafka, disco).",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 20,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "health_status{job=\"xcommerce-microservices\"}",
          "legendFormat": "health {{ instance }} {{ status }}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}